      <title>新兴市场股票随着美国关税的担忧而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/emerging-currencies-steady-after-china-data-with-us-tariffs-eyed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者急切地离开唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的全球关税计划，新兴市场的股票连续第三天暴跌。]]></description>
